        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">See how to embed the widget in your pages with code examples.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="https://github.com/Devometric/devometric-platform/blob/main/docs/API_SPECIFICATION.md" target="_blank" class="group bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700 hover:border-emerald-500/50 rounded-xl p-6 transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-500/10">
